<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1444644>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. A–B: Field sites within Parque Nacional Cusuco, inhabited by Eucynorta rooneyi sp. nov. A. Field site near to base camp, at approximately 1600 m asl. B. Field site near to a temporary camp, approximately 1800 m asl. C. Live male of Eucynorta rooneyi sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1444644/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1444638>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Dorsal scutum and venter of Eucynorta rooneyi sp. nov., holotype male (MZSP 71769); inverse coloring was used to show markings on dorsal scutum. A. Dorsal view. B. Ventral view. C. Lateral view. Scale bars = 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1444638/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1444640>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Appendages of Eucynorta rooneyi sp. nov., holotype male (MZSP 71769). A. Chelicerae, anterior view. B–D, Left pedipalp, B. Dorsal view. C. Lateral view. D. Ventral view. E–F. Leg IV, from trochanter to tibia. E. Ventral view. F. Dorsal view. Scale bars = 1 mm (A–D), 3 mm (E–F)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1444640/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1444642>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Distal portion of penis and ovipositor of Eucynorta rooneyi sp. nov. A–C: Penis (MZSP 71769). A. Lateral view. B. Dorsal view. C. Ventral view. D–F: Ovipositor (MZSP 71770), with ds to the left. D. Lateral view. E. Apical view. F. Magnified view of setae. Scale bars = 100 µm (A–C); 50 µm (D–F)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1444642/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

